        $(document).ready(function () {
            //Set NaicsCodeSelected to readonly
            $('#ContentPlaceHolder1_txtNaicsCodeSelected').attr('readonly', 'readonly');
            $('#ContentPlaceHolder1_txtNaicsCodeSelected').css('background', '#CFCFCF');

            //Reset values and appearances
            ResetCountyCityPddZip();
        });

        function SetCountyCityPddZipReadonly(controlName) {

            //alert($('#' + controlName).val());
            var regexCounty = /County/;
            var regexPDD = /PDD/;
            var regexCity = /City/;
            var regexZipCode = /ZipCode/;

            if ( ($('#ContentPlaceHolder1_ddlCounty option:selected').val() == '') && ($('#ContentPlaceHolder1_ddlPDD option:selected').val() == '') &&
                ($('#ContentPlaceHolder1_ddlCity option:selected').val() == '') && ($('#ContentPlaceHolder1_txtZipCode').val() == '')) {
                ResetCountyCityPddZip();
            } else {

                var resetCounter = 0;
                ($('#ContentPlaceHolder1_ddlCounty option:selected').val() != '') ? resetCounter++ : 0;
                ($('#ContentPlaceHolder1_ddlPDD option:selected').val() != '') ? resetCounter++ : 0;
                ($('#ContentPlaceHolder1_ddlCity option:selected').val() != '') ? resetCounter++ : 0;
                ($('#ContentPlaceHolder1_txtZipCode').val() != '') ? resetCounter++ : 0;

                if (resetCounter < 2) {
                    $('#ContentPlaceHolder1_ddlCounty').attr('disabled', 'disabled');
                    $('#ContentPlaceHolder1_ddlCounty').css('background', '#CFCFCF');
                    $('#ContentPlaceHolder1_ddlPDD').attr('disabled', 'disabled');
                    $('#ContentPlaceHolder1_ddlPDD').css('background', '#CFCFCF');
                    $('#ContentPlaceHolder1_ddlCity').attr('disabled', 'disabled');
                    $('#ContentPlaceHolder1_ddlCity').css('background', '#CFCFCF');
                    $('#ContentPlaceHolder1_txtZipCode').attr('disabled', 'disabled');
                    $('#ContentPlaceHolder1_txtZipCode').css('background', '#CFCFCF');

                    if (regexCounty.test(controlName)) {
                            $('#ContentPlaceHolder1_ddlCounty').removeAttr('disabled');
                            $('#ContentPlaceHolder1_ddlCounty').css('background', '#FFFFFF');
                    }

                    if (regexPDD.test(controlName)) {
                            $('#ContentPlaceHolder1_ddlPDD').removeAttr('disabled');
                            $('#ContentPlaceHolder1_ddlPDD').css('background', '#FFFFFF');
                    }

                    if (regexCity.test(controlName)) {
                            $('#ContentPlaceHolder1_ddlCity').removeAttr('disabled');
                            $('#ContentPlaceHolder1_ddlCity').css('background', '#FFFFFF');
                    }

                    if (regexZipCode.test(controlName)) {
                            $('#ContentPlaceHolder1_txtZipCode').removeAttr('disabled');
                            $('#ContentPlaceHolder1_txtZipCode').css('background', '#FFFFFF');
                    }
                }
            }
        }

        function ResetCountyCityPddZip() {
            $('#ContentPlaceHolder1_ddlCounty').removeAttr('disabled');
            $('#ContentPlaceHolder1_ddlCounty').css('background', '#FFFFFF');
            $('#ContentPlaceHolder1_ddlCounty option:selected').removeAttr('selected');
            $('#ContentPlaceHolder1_ddlCounty').val('');
            $('#ContentPlaceHolder1_ddlPDD').removeAttr('disabled');
            $('#ContentPlaceHolder1_ddlPDD').css('background', '#FFFFFF');
            $('#ContentPlaceHolder1_ddlPDD option:selected').removeAttr('selected');
            $('#ContentPlaceHolder1_ddlPDD').val('');
            $('#ContentPlaceHolder1_ddlCity').removeAttr('disabled');
            $('#ContentPlaceHolder1_ddlCity').css('background', '#FFFFFF');
            $('#ContentPlaceHolder1_ddlCity option:selected').removeAttr('selected');
            $('#ContentPlaceHolder1_ddlCity').val('');
            $('#ContentPlaceHolder1_txtZipCode').removeAttr('disabled');
            $('#ContentPlaceHolder1_txtZipCode').css('background', '#FFFFFF');
            $('#ContentPlaceHolder1_txtZipCode').val('');
        }

        function FindNaicsCodes() {
            var thisitem;
            thisitem = document.getElementById("ContentPlaceHolder1_txtNaicsSearch");

            var thiscode = thisitem.value;

            if (thiscode == 'No items found matching input' || thisitem.value == '') {
                thisitem.value = '';
                return false;
            }
            var ncode = "";
            var ndesc = "";
            var arr = thiscode.split("| ");
            // try to trap when an item is not picked from the list here.           
            if (arr.length != 2) {
                thisitem.value = '';
                return false;
            }
            ncode = arr[0];
            ndesc = arr[1];
            ncode = ncode.trim();
            ndesc = ndesc.trim();

            var txtbox = $find("ContentPlaceHolder1_txtNaicsCodeSelected");
            $('#ContentPlaceHolder1_txtNaicsCodeSelected').val(thiscode.trim());

            //listbox.get_items().add(item);

            thisitem.value = ''

        }


        function NaicsCodeSelected(sender, args) {
            var mydl = $find("ContentPlaceHolder1_txtNaicsCodeSelected");
            args.IsValid = mydl.val().length().trim() > 0;

        }

        function ClearlblMessage2() {
            $('#ContentPlaceHolder1_lblMessage2').text("");
        }
